>> about the package <<

     LEBEN.EXE : main program, written in Pascal
     LEBEN.LIF : the default datafile of <life pattern>s
     LEBEN.HLP : help you to understand and play this simulation
     LEBEN.HLC : chinese version of LEBEN.HLP
     LEBEN.DOC : this file
     LEBEN.DCC : chinese version of LEBEN.DOC
    (LEBEN.PRN): the output file of <life pattern>s


>> about the version <<

     1.0 : 1993.4.25
           for MONO TEXT 80x25 mode
           function : Quit, Move cursor, Toggle, Clean, Run, Stop
     2.0 : 1994.1.24
           for COLOR TEXT 80x50 mode
           advance : menu, Run, Stop
           add : title, hide cursor, show gen. sum name, end, LEBEN.LIF
                 Random, Step, Load, Save, List
     2.5 : 1994.3.2
           for COLOR TEXT 80x25 mode
           delete : end, show name
           advance : title, menu, LEBEN.LIF
                     Run, Random, Load, Save, List
           add : show number, LEBEN.HLP, LEBEN.DOC. (LEBEN.PRN)
                 Help, Next, Info, Print, Center
     3.0 : 1994.4.4
           for COLOR TEXT 80x25 or 80x50 or chinese mode
           delete : List, Center, show number
           advance : Info->Exp, Run->Grow, Clean->Clear, Load, Save, Random
                     menu, characters, LEBEN.LIF, LEBEN.HLP, LEBEN.DOC
           add : Step, Delete, Name, Find, Rotate,
                 sound, mouse, chinese, parameter
     3.1 : 1994.4.30
           for CGA,EGA,VGA,VGA+ text mode or CGA chinese mode
           delete : Delete, (LEBEN.BAK)
           advance : menu, mouse, beep, parameter, Help, Explain,
                     LEBEN.LIF, LEBEN.HLP, LEBEN.DOC
           add : lawfulcheck, Get, Put, View, Mirrow
     3.2 : 1994.5.21
           for CGA,EGA,VGA,VGA+ text mode or CGA chinese mode
           advance : mouse, LEBEN.LIF
     X.X : XXXX.X.X
           for all mode
           add : other rules, discover


